<title>Sweden, August 2001</title>
<center><h2>Sweden, August 2001</h2>
Chang in front of Rok-stone (left) and Gota canal (right)
<br>
<img src="slab3.jpg" width=300>
<img src="sgota2.jpg" width=300>
